This is an option to set the log file retention period.

Valid values can be set from 0 to 365, and the unit of the set value is one day.

The default value of 0 does not delete log files.

If the option is set as follows, log files older than 7 days from today are deleted.

    ex) log_max_age = 7


---

  * Default : 0
  * Type : Number
  * Restart : not required
  * Version supported : 5.6.1.22